HEADWORD: Astigmatic
<hw>As`tig*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Med. &
Opt.)</fld> <def>Affected with, or pertaining to, astigmatism; <as>as,
<ex>astigmatic</ex> eyes</as>; also, remedying astigmatism; <as>as,
<ex>astigmatic</ex> lenses</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Astigmatism</ent>⟦br⟧
